This project contains playbooks to deploy the NFS server which will be storing the data and the web 
server or here we can say NFS client server to serve the static content when the users send the 
request to the web server. The deployment is fully automated with ansible playbooks and roles.

The code for website is stored in NFS server in location /var/indanikrishna for my sitewhich we will
be mounting on the apache web server. This location contain index.html file.

Further, the ansible playbook and roles for the installation of MariaDB Server is also there.
In this case we install and configure the MariaDB server and restore the backup file to see 
the server is fully functioning.
